title: The Richest Person in History | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 32
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The babes are back and are talking richest people in history! The episode starts with Chris telling the story of how he BOMBED his stand up comedy set for the Met's owner Steve Cohen's birthday. Chris can't say Impossible. Do any words have in instead of im? How much money would you need to never work ever again? Who was the richest person to ever live on Earth? How many billionaires are on Earth right now? Cristiano Ronaldo Causes Coca-Cola's Value to Plummet $4 Billion. What's going on with Steven Seagal? Steven Seagal has left the US and became a big part of Russia. Steven Seagal is close friends with Vladimir Putin?! Chris has seen Sal get mad before. You ever realize that at one point in your life you were better at basketball than Lebron? Sal went on a tour of Australia. Wedding horror stories! Why is common law married a thing? Is broad bad to call a woman? Can you call your girlfriend the old bag? SHOUT OUT TOM BRADY!!!!
Rate us on iTunes!
